title: I travelled across the world to make this Warhammer Diorama
description:
Head to https://squarespace.com/squidmar to save 10% off your first purchase of a website or domain using code squidmar

This week, we travel across the world - to collaborate with @Jazza and @TabletopTime to make this epic diorama in a challenge worthy of the historybooks... or something! But at least we got to have some fun with art and creativity and make an awesome warhammer diorama in the process!
